# Fix Game Crash & Stability Issues

### [Critical Stability & Audio Fixes]

- **Audio Resilience**: [AudioManager](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/utils/audio_manager.dart#5-82) will now use a global try-catch that silently ignores *any* sound errors. This prevents missing asset files from crashing the match-day simulation sequence.
- **Navigation Safety**: Refactoring the `/game` route in [main.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/main.dart) to use a more stable state management approach, preventing the `FutureBuilder` from accidentally resetting the game when `SharedPreferences` updates.
- **Type Safety (Web)**: Fixing `Team.fromJson` to use [(json['strength'] as num).toDouble()](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/utils/settings_manager.dart#12-18) to avoid potential `double` vs [int](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/stat_rings.dart#38-56) cast errors on Flutter Web.
- **Swipe Guard**: Adding a `_isProcessing` flag to [GameScreen](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#22-28) to prevent double-clicks/swipes from triggering multiple matches or logic loops simultaneously.
- **Ticker Logic**: Correcting the Phase 0 message bug in [_runRemainingSegments](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#298-317).

The goal is to resolve the game crashes reported by the user, specifically focusing on improper resource management, missing routes, and inefficient UI updates.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Navigation & Routing

#### [MODIFY] [main.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/main.dart)
- Add named routes for `/game` to prevent crashes when using `Navigator.pushReplacementNamed`.
- Ensure all required parameters are passed correctly.

### [Component] Game Logic & Safety

#### [MODIFY] [game_screen.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart)
- Add `if (!mounted) return;` checks to all [Timer](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/screens/game_screen.dart#209-221) and `Future` callbacks that call `setState`.
- Remove the unused `_audioPlayer` instance.
- Cache the `SharedPreferences` instance during initialization to reduce overhead.
- Ensure the `_gameTimer` is consistently cancelled in all exit paths.

#### [MODIFY] [manager_mood.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/manager_mood.dart)
- Fix threshold bug: update 70/50/30 to 0.7/0.5/0.3 to match the normalized double values.

### [Component] UI Optimization

#### [MODIFY] [breaking_news_ticker.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/breaking_news_ticker.dart)
- Reduce the frequency of `Timer.periodic` and `animateTo` duration to improve performance (e.g., from 50ms to 100ms or more).
- Cache the joined message string instead of re-joining it in every build/item builder call.

### [Component] Audio Management

#### [MODIFY] [audio_manager.dart](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/utils/audio_manager.dart)
- Improve error handling for `UrlSource` to prevent potential hangs.
- (Optional but recommended) Suggest moving match sounds to local assets for offline stability.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `flutter analyze` to ensure no linting regressions.
- Verify that `Navigator.pushReplacementNamed(context, '/game')` no longer crashes in a mock environment (if possible).

### Manual Verification
- Start a new career and play several games to ensure stability.
- Use the "RESUME CAREER" button to verify the new named route works correctly.
- Observe the "Manager Mood" widget to ensure it updates images correctly based on performance.
- Check the [BreakingNewsTicker](file:///Users/amolsehgal/antigravity%20-%20touchline%20tantrum/touchline_tantrum/lib/widgets/breaking_news_ticker.dart#5-11) for smooth scrolling without UI lag.
